M834 80h400000v40h-400000z"></path></svg></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1908em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>具体公式书写方法：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e74eb43960a1">https://www.jianshu.com/p/e74eb43960a1</a></p>
<h2 id="表格">表格</h2>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|昨天|今天|明天|</span><br><span class="line">|:---|---:|:---:|</span><br><span class="line">|a|b|c|</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:left">昨天</th>
<th style="text-align:right">今天</th>
<th style="text-align:center">明天</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">a</td>
<td style="text-align:right">b</td>
<td style="text-align:center">c</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2 id="脚注">脚注</h2>
<p>格式如：<code>408圣经[^408] </code><br>
下方要对其解释，格式为:<code>[^408]: 机组，计网，OS，DS</code><br>
408圣经[^408]<br>
[^408]: 机组，计网，OS，DS</p>
<p>##横线分割</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">giao!!!!</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<hr>
<p>giao!!!</p>
<h2 id="web跳转链接">web跳转链接</h2>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度](https:<span class="comment">//www.bilibili.com/ "挂羊头卖狗肉")</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/" title="挂羊头卖狗肉">百度</a><br>
括号里面的字在鼠标放在链接字体上悬停的时候会提示该字<br>
当然直接给出url也可以识别</p>
<h2 id="锚链接">锚链接</h2>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">跳转[Markdown使用说明](#Markdown使用说明)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p>跳转<a href="#Markdown%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E">Markdown使用说明</a></p>
<h2 id="图片插入">图片插入</h2>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![picture](/img/PageFeng.jpg <span class="string">"tip"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p>里面的路径可以改为本地链接<br>
<img src="/img/PageFeng.jpg" alt="picture" title="tip"></p>
<h2 id="字体">字体</h2>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*斜体* **加粗** `<span class="built_in">printf</span>()` :smile H~<span class="number">2</span>~O x^<span class="number">2</span>^ ==highlight==</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p><em>斜体</em> <strong>加粗</strong> <code>printf()</code> :smile H~2~O x^2^ ==highlight==</p>
]]></content>
